Koyaanisqatsi. (2018). Marlon Brando - Interview (June 12, 1973). YouTube. URL [ https://substack.com/redirect/0f4c32df-6310-4a31-9033-d95a95e16e20?j=eyJ1IjoiODNyODBiIn0.OKQowPztAkooRPZOSJH51DYSzfDD6iDDx4smP5_rvZc ]
