React Native Evals

Our suite of evaluations for coding React Native apps got quite popular after Composer 2 model from Cursor nailing it with 96% score and gaining the first place.

Since then, the team was hard at work to add 2 new categories, 4 new models, and a bunch of automations so we can add new models quickly, like we did with Opus 4.7 providing a benchmark for it one day after the public release.

We consider this project only the beginning, and would love to make it the most comprehensive benchmark for agents generating React Native code.

It’s open source and we encourage you to add more, and more complex, cases that you see agents often fail to accomplish up to the latest standards.

