React Native core contributions

Kamil is getting closer to finalize CSS calc support in React Native. A few smaller PRs landed in both Yoga and React Native, and there are a few more to go. Apart from basic calc support for width, height, etc., it now composes into more CSS properties, animations, and transitions.

It’s both an exciting and humbling contribution as getting a small functionality like this may take many months to ship in the React Native core.

