Britannica Editors (2026). Dick Fosbury. Encyclopedia Britannica. URL [ https://substack.com/redirect/9c289e94-b04c-41a1-917e-ffdc5cfcdd2c?j=eyJ1IjoiODNyODBiIn0.OKQowPztAkooRPZOSJH51DYSzfDD6iDDx4smP5_rvZc ]
